The **live** player-facing primer is `instinct-rpg-primer-v2.html`, embedded in Card Studio via the
**Player Primer** tab (`index.html` → iframe). Older `instinct-rpg-primer*.html` files are not live
unless Annie explicitly switches the iframe.

