## In scope (summary)

Deck/hand philosophy, basic checks (Build/Roll/Read), Hit Dice intro, card types at a glance, how a
card plays, 21-card chargen flow, keyword glossary, playtest FAQ. GM defers Contests, Threat, Resolve,
Snap Check procedure — see teach-the-table rule.

## Ship checklist

1. Visual pass on **all** chargen samples (especially Core pair).
2. Commit + push `main` per `instinct-git.mdc`.
3. No Baserow push unless card HTML changed (`instinct-agent-ops.mdc`).
4. Share live link:
